{"tid":2300110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊︱周父呼籲見效 多次於現場出現少年已錄取口供","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:20:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"90b8258f803ca619eecc199cd0d19832595fcace","tid":2300110,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"科大男生周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突中，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲，死因研訊繼續。死因裁判官高偉雄臨散庭前表示，昨日透露有資料提供的新一名市民，警方昨晚已完成錄取口供，死因庭已初步收到證供，他打算與研訊主任大律師葉志康翻查閉路電視，「想睇下見唔見到佢」，又謂「大概都知佢係邊個㗎喇！」稱是從停車場三樓跑到二樓半的戴帽少年。<br />\n<br />\n綜合連日證供，此人相信是停車場及行人天橋閉路電視曾拍到多次出現的戴白帽少年，他由三樓跑往二樓半時，剛巧有兩名消防員由二樓半行落二樓，雙方被牆壁阻隔，陰差陽錯下未有發現對方。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊明續。庭外了解，明天會繼續傳召升降台車上的消防員作供，如有時間或會傳召義務急救員。至於該名報料市民，則仍在安排出庭時間，亦有機會明天傳召。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/KVWCZUF5GRFPNK6SOJTQSXQIQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FKVWCZUF5GRFPNK6SOJTQSXQIQY%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=a10560b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FKVWCZUF5GRFPNK6SOJTQSXQIQY%2F&h=5c229083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/KVWCZUF5GRFPNK6SOJTQSXQIQY/</a>"},{"pid":"6c6b57bd8a989f4f583c9c0bc87e240e8117acf9","tid":2300110,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f954c72c330bbcd415f231615324f3f19da2d9b0","tid":2300110,"uid":152258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"好想知呢D人落完口供會唔會比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58002930f2177be2fb1023a4c6b4d5f505f66f9"